### HYMN VII

#### Praise of the Ādityas

<span class="margnote"><span id="an_0700701">1</span></span>I have sung
praise to Diti's sons and Aditi's, those very lofty and  
   invulnerable Gods.  
  For far within the depths of ocean is their home and in the wor-  
   ship paid them none excelleth these.

